    <detaileddescription>
<para>Standard system time functions</para>
<para>This module contains standard time functions and formatters for printing. Note that Pebble now supports both local time and UTC time (including timezones and daylight savings time). Most of these functions are part of the C standard library which is documented at <ulink url="https://sourceware.org/newlib/libc.html#Timefns">https://sourceware.org/newlib/libc.html#Timefns</ulink> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
